version_description:
- Option to have all panels appear at start
- Add poor connection option for degraded saturation

- Fixed bug where RR did not activate (Thank you, Dan)
- Fixed "Touch to refresh BP" when using IBP

- Ability to send images to monitor
- Connection hints

Minor updates and additions.
Basic image transfers.

Due to changes in iOS, devices running iOS 9.3.5 will not connect to devices with iOS 10 or newer.
- Fixed sharing bug on iPhone - document browser was not being presented

- Defibrillator artefact
- CPR option in settings
